    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Part of the outworks of a fortress, built in front of the glacis, consisting of two converging faces forming a salient angle, forming an arrowhead shape.Similar to a redan, but with faces forming an acute angle.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
